onfirms they lose, V5a is validated.\n- Negative funding deepening is bullish \u2014 3 consecutive periods of increasing shorts. If BTC holds $67,500+ through Asian session, expect squeeze move toward $69K during London open (11h). This would give strong negative bias signals = good YES-only trades.\n- Regime needs to stay MIXED or drop to RANGE by 11h. Currently MIXED 3/6, right on the edge.\n\n**Decision:**\n- V5a shadow validator LIVE on cron \u2014 no code changes needed, purely observational\n- Trading outlook for today: BULLISH (negative funding squeeze + MIXED regime likely \u2192 RANGE by 11h)\n- Estimated 2-4 trades if regime cooperates, $15-30 P&L target\n- HL positions: HOLD (all slightly green, waiting for Hani approval on consolidation)\n\n**Next:** P4 \u2014 After active hours, analyze first batch of V5a shadow data. Also check if indicator logging finally works on first Apr 1 trade (critical zombie-bug verification).\n\n---\n## 2026-03-31 19:38 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] VWAP Redeemed: +30pp Delta on n=250 \u2014 Remove Decision REVERSED\n\n**Task:** Analyze 19h conviction failures + ",
